Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.77,0:00:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.27,0:00:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.98,0:00:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绕过危险的转角 追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.42,0:00:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.33,0:00:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.90,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.11,0:00:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.65,0:01:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.26,0:01:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.59,0:01:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.16,0:01:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.83,0:01:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.64,0:01:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻壳机动队 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在茅葺总理正握手欢迎休雷德国务卿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次大战后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.49,0:02:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美帝以强大军事国家之姿夸示其力量至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在随着经济破产所带来的国力下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.87,0:02:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了探讨日本主导下的安保再缔结案的草案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.10,0:02:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧急派遣国务卿到日本来表现出不顾身段的应对方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是日本政府如果看看国内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,景气的不安定感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民对策的迟延
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及宪法第9条问题等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,9条问题：日本自诩为“和平宪法”中涉及战争放弃原则的第9条所引起的争议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,课题也堆积如山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.98,0:02:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来自各方面的抗议行动必定会逐渐激化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要连休息时间都看这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.39,0:02:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算输到脱裤子也不要迁怒到别人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没资格说我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次我赢定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.35,0:03:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,＃14  小心左眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我问你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么事到如今还要签订安全保障呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本不是也有军队吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的政府虽然是超级鹰派政权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 正因为现在美帝经济萧条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.47,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才想在自己掌握主导权的状态下缔结安保条约啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是想洗刷前世纪的屈辱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前世纪的屈辱是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛...简单来说就是战败的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.55,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上宪法第9条这个不确定的装置目前还在运作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.55,0:03:53.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本国宪法第9条：日本国民真诚地企望以正义和秩序为基调的国际和平\N永远放弃国家主权发动的战争、武力威胁或使用武力作为解决国际争端的手段\N为达此目的，日本不保持陆海空军和其他战争力量，不承认国家交战权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自卫军不能公开出去外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能拥有核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然前世纪的安保是在屈辱之下达成协议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.90,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 美国当矛日本当盾的不可分默契还是运作良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.87,0:04:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是到现在因为看到经济问题这个新的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.38,0:04:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以一定是想来达成互补彼此弱点的协议吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是成熟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的资料让我同步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.66,0:04:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没什么不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是说不要吵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是很认真的对决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我闭上嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.56,0:04:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛 连阿东都这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明还是新人 这样不会太傲慢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.07,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一直输也不要怪到别人头上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会全部赢回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.58,0:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不这样就不好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梭哈再怎么说也是机率的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么都是斋藤先生赢呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从刚才开始也非常在意这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其以现在用的规则来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要先记住所有人的牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后从第一张和最后一张 预测对方手上的牌就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.24,0:05:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必然都是斋藤先生赢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道为什么 最后都是斋藤先生拿走筹码啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.18,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只因为他很会唬人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快我就会撕掉他那张面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那叫做扑克脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.59,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要记住喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们办不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.46,0:05:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起我经历过的生死关头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梭哈只不过是小孩子的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还真敢说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.43,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我承认你是一流的狙击手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.77,0:05:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 那就算能拿来跟梭哈比 还是没什么说服力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟让我打心底发抖的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.85,0:05:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一对一做狙击对决的经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.68,0:05:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从来没有像当时那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.99,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得跟对手打心理战很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.73,0:06:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,体验过那次对决以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通家伙心里想的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一眼就能够预测出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种话很难以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺便问一下\N那是什么样的对手呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想听吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—想听！想听！—想听！想听！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都跟的话 我就说给你们听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不是想听你的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是2020年夏天的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欧亚大陆上每天进行着毫无意义的消耗战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于我不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.60,0:06:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本在奇妙的政治平衡夹缝中享受着归罪于他人的锁国状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.94,0:07:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我以佣兵的身份加入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.28,0:07:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟墨西哥临时政权同一阵线的义勇军“赤色之白”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.05,0:07:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且当时我的左眼还平安无事待在眼窝里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中东的石油和南美的毒品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有特权的地方经常都有纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在先前的核大战中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分裂且疲惫不已的美帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.81,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始认真考虑借由消灭新大陆的毒品市场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抑制国家预算的无谓流失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在打倒墨西哥贪污政权的名义下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美帝煽动联合国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.06,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派遣英日混编的联合国军到南美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先以迅速攻占首都为理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按惯例进行地毯式轰炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来甚至为了肃清抵抗的游击队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.84,0:08:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出派机械化师团到蒙特雷的野蛮事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轰炸之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的伙伴被联合国军的装甲部队全灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我则一直在寻找适当的投降机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在这时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.95,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,监听敌方通信的终端机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉我即将跟持有战术核武器的特殊部队接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今无法拿出辉煌战果的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心想就做做薪水份内的工作 顺便换取紧张感这个礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.34,0:08:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对胆敢带来战术核武器这种可怕东西的不法之徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.24,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真心想要给予他们来自神之视线的恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.65,0:09:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太过在意关于攻击医疗机构和教会的批判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下太多游击队可以潜伏的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是应该有两个小队在歼灭残党
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是这样就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本上你们都太粗枝大叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.34,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们英国人是不是太过度信仰SAS的传说呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,约翰兰搏吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.76,0:10:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.21,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有狙击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.97,0:10:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趴下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川 先假设是使用卫星的狙击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侵入卫星找出敌人的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.95,0:10:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.65,0:10:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大妈伍长 不要动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有使用卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半径1公里内有大范围干扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能从干扰的发射源算出对方的位置吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.73,0:10:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经在做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.10,0:10:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身手很好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是老兵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有时间说废话还不给我去搜索敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是菜鸟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从哪一边射过来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够确认吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会被敌人听到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改成电子脑通讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.81,0:10:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己用用看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会被杂音吓一跳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.02,0:10:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.98,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太大意了 完全掌握不到敌人的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不快点救他的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.02,0:11:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 中士 怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老姜!我们全体掩护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.73,0:11:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁这个空档救出大妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白雪去帮忙老姜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏心的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 日本的那几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们负责西侧建筑物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的人负责东侧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 你会得救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.79,0:11:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.09,0:11:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.79,0:11:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西侧的建筑物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.50,0:11:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得让他们暂时搞不清楚我在哪里才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流点冷汗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20厘米吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！停止射击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.89,0:12:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老姜从什么方向被击中的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么傻话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没看到刚刚车子被打翻吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人在东边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 被包围的可能性很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川 干扰来自哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然是大概估计 有3个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个是东边的建筑物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外两个应该是教堂和医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得东边是诱饵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多半是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20厘米打过来之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干扰有一瞬间的中断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且背对太阳是基本概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.73,0:12:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.59,0:12:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,东边是诱饵而且多半没人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被包围了应该会开更多枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定对方只有狙击手一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么能这么肯定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,状况这么告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有一个提议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在绕过东边的建筑物 到那边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现建筑物里面没人之后 我会给你信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.35,0:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后大家一起朝教堂和医院攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.08,0:13:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁这个时候回收伍长和战术核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去那个的话我们将会进退两难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 你和白雪两个人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迂回之后再会合吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们马上会发现东边没人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这之前再减少一个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.01,0:13:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大妈你不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然没人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很细心地只装了一发子弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能大意的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过敌人多半只有一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.81,0:14:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用人数优势压迫他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狙击手在教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口气攻下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 他说不定在医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为干扰曾经停止过一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.51,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算剔除无法认定有发射机的废墟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能放掉医院这条线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道那边到这里的直线距离有几公尺吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.99,0:14:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定在教堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何如此肯定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙可是故意连GPS都不用 纯粹以狙击技术来攻击我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他是个熟知科里奥利法则的高手 所有人都会被杀掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:35.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Coriolis Effect:因惯性和地球自转作用对移动物体的影响导致的复杂系统\N一直被使用在现代狙击技术之中\N由法国力学家科里奥利在1835年提出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,选哪一边不都可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.87,0:14:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.14,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在战场上比起勇猛 慎重才是长命的秘诀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看那个母猩猩怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的职业高手就是指她那样的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母猩猩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.92,0:14:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.03,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.73,0:15:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人在医院里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先把箱子收回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伍长已经太迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 暂时先撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以在这种地方全灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么傻话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡菜被干掉了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要报仇 我要杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先撤退之后再回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要撤退也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论选哪一条路 我们都得跟狙击手作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然无法通讯 我们也无法呼叫援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还有人数上的优势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.48,0:15:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的同伴也被打死了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 进攻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.29,0:16:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.26,0:16:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有发生恐慌 就马上重新组织攻势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有个优秀的指挥官在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.90,0:16:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道决战的时刻已经接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧张感一口气提高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每一个细胞都感觉的到肾上腺素的分泌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.45,0:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战场上的杀戮并不知道谁杀了谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 其中有个唯一的例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是狙击手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.69,0:16:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狙击行为本身从一开始就替你发出了名片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以只有狙击手不会成为俘虏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为杀死伙伴和指挥官的仇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.93,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命中注定会被当场格杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.84,0:17:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无后座力炮击中大楼之后 大量发射烟雾弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藏在烟雾里面冲进大楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.95,0:17:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.99,0:17:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 你们掩护我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟白雪冲进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能当掩护的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是很好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要想成她很信赖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.11,0:17:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交给少校吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后面那家伙会想办法解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还被叫作母猩猩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只知道她是战斗的天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.89,0:17:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们叫她少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.10,0:18:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只跟少校对峙短短不到一秒钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.21,0:18:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就马上想象到这次对射的结果而全身发抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.21,0:18:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我身为狙击手的经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想定各种状况之后得到的结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.58,0:18:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会被干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.59,0:18:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从她把步枪枪拖抵在腰部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼睛一眨也不眨的动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上知道她是全身义体的义体人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.63,0:19:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且手上是全感应式的半自动步枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然长、中、短距离的射击控制软件全都有安装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.34,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我尝试在想象当中对少校发射一发子弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.69,0:19:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一发子弹被少校击落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用手动栓式枪机的我想躲到柱子后面的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二发就会击中我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管模拟几次都是一样的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是可是 再这样下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 再这样下去早晚会被干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.14,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拼命想要怎么样才能逆转这个局势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.18,0:19:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后我注意到某样东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.81,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是少校刚开始击中的干扰装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.78,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校为何一开始不惜花3发子弹去破坏那个东西呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.05,0:19:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道说她没有安装中距离的射击控制软件?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 一定是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她虽然担任狙击手这个位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却把全感应式的步枪改成短枪管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是为了中距离时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.57,0:20:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以拿来代替机枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么她要跟我在这里对射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就需要控制软件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正从卫星下载控制软件吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.02,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要来得及啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙技术不差嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.04,0:20:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从现在起当我的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从一开始就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.15,0:20:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.35,0:20:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从一开始就被少校的扑克脸骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.48,0:21:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我没有拒绝的权利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.19,0:21:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是少校下达的第一个命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.87,0:21:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我最后一张牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故事虽然有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过跟这场赌局无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我赌手上所有的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也赌全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.48,0:21:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逞强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有这次你无法靠唬人来赢得胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要的是黑桃的同花大顺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.16,0:21:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 你什么牌都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.00,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为黑桃A早就在我这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没有胜算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且刚刚的话也是骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故事虽然有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.24,0:21:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 我记得在以前某部电影看过类似的情节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.38,0:22:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 全部都是编的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就玩到这里为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,东 记得算清楚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.30,0:22:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得不好意思了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.10,0:22:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 新人 先垫一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.34,0:22:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是任性的前辈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.44,0:22:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斋藤先生真的什么都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.71,0:22:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快看快看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.95,0:22:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斋藤先生最后用黑桃九完成了同花顺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.25,0:22:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.16,0:22:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说刚刚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.06,0:22:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.73,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.41,0:23:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.12,0:23:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.69,0:23:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.60,0:23:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.97,0:23:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.31,0:23:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.61,0:23:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.18,0:23:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我审视自身—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.15,0:23:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.45,0:23:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.82,0:23:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去让这一切成真的—它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.83,0:24:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.97,0:24:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.20,0:24:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.84,0:24:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我审视自身—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.84,0:24:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.18,0:24:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.52,0:24:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去让这一切成真的—它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.56,0:24:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在这个躯壳里

